---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for the Hunger Games Simulator website."
>
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-display font-bold mb-8 mt-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p class="mb-6">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">1. Information Collection</h2>
      <p>We collect minimal information through Google Analytics:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
        <li>Pages visited on our website</li>
        <li>Time spent on site</li>
        <li>Referring websites</li>
        <li>Browser type and device information</li>
        <li>General location data (country/region level only)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>The collected analytics data is used solely for:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
        <li>Understanding website traffic patterns</li>
        <li>Improving user experience</li>
        <li>Website performance optimization</li>
        <li>Content development decisions</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">3. Data Storage and Security</h2>
      <p>Important information about data handling:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
        <li>All simulation data is stored locally in your browser</li>
        <li>No personal data is transmitted to or stored on our servers</li>
        <li>We do not use cookies except those required by Google Analytics</li>
        <li>We do not collect or store any personally identifiable information</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We use the following third-party service:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
        <li>Google Analytics for website usage analytics</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Google Analytics data collection can be controlled through your browser settings and opt-out tools.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">5. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>Our service is intended for general audiences. We do not knowingly collect data from children under 13 years of age.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">6. Changes to Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">7. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You have the right to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
        <li>Opt out of Google Analytics tracking</li>
        <li>Request information about the data we collect</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your analytics data</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">8. Contact Information</h2>
      <p>For privacy-related questions or concerns, please contact us at: <a href="mailto:colorepistle@gmail.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">colorepistle@gmail.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout> 